Hidden Packages<br>
<br>
When you see the ROCKSTER billboard, there are usually some items nearby. On the 3 islands, hidden packages are usually found near the billboards. For every 10 hidden packages you find, you gain access to a new weapon located at your hideout, free of charge. <br>
