This Cheat/Hint submitted by Mark Padilla on Tuesday, November 13, 2001 at 19:09:01 <br>
Bonus Buggy<br>
<br>
Successfully complete the Mafia missions to unlock the Buggy. Return to the Portland and go to the Diablo parking lot (where the mission phone is located) between 19:00 to 24:00 to find the same Buggy glimpsed in Joey's garage from the Mafia mission. It will appear in the same location &amp; change color each time.<br>
