<br>
For one, the PS2 cant handle &quot;portland and staunton island&quot; put together, this is why there is a &quot;now entering ______ island&quot; loading screen because theres not enough ram in the PS2 to handle both cities. And you cant have every car on screen at the same time in the &quot;infinite car&quot; garage, there isnt enough ram. If you want to see how ram works, then just do the tank cheat code abunch of times, after about the 7th tank ALL cars will be gone because the tanks take up all the ram the ps2 has set for cars, and since for some reason the tanks dont disapear like normal cars do, you can drive around the whole city without any cars on the road.<br>
<br>
